title: WATCHMEN Episode 2 Breakdown, Theories and Details You Missed!
author: Think Story
comment: Guess what I got you for Christmas? 5:28 🎁
Did anyone else notice Grandpa Will reach into the boiled egg water like it was nothing? maybe he is Dr. Manhattan.

pretty sure Angela is the only black person at Judd's house, that's... suspicious

I think you missed the implication of how Angela was saved: 
Someone stands over Angela, cut to close up of Angela's face, Cut to close up of Judd's face. To me this implies Judd was the person holding the gun to Angela's face. Whether he was part of the cavalry or maybe he was undercover, who knows, but my guess is that he probably saved Angela.
